  ('medical-tech-moex-05150', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-110-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於16S-23S rRNA gene internal transcribed spacer（ITS）定序法的敘述，下列何者正確？ A. 在ITS中只有一個tRNA基因', '["", "ITS在同種（species）間相似度低", "對不動桿菌屬（Acinetobacter）而言，優於16S rRNA基因定序鑑定法", "每種細菌只有一段ITS序列，長度固定"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:22+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d0c3b6cd970e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "442605fb8f96", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110100", "c": "308", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "110", "exam_name": "第一梯次:110年第二次專技牙醫師第二階段、藥師第二階段、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師考試、110 年專技職能治療師、呼吸治療師、獸醫師、助產師考...", "original_question_number": 56, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
